text: FIFA International Soccer is a 1993 association football simulation video game in Electronic Arts' FIFA series published by Electronic Arts. It was released for the Sega Genesis, Sega CD, Game Gear, Master System, Super Nintendo, Game Boy, 3DO, MS-DOS and Amiga.
